RelevantSubjects.Html:
If you're working in the furniture industry, you may be able to start on a furniture product developer advanced apprenticeship.

You could also do a product design and development degree apprenticeship.
You could do an accident repair technician or vehicle damage paint technician advanced apprenticeship.

You can work towards this role by starting with an intermediate apprenticeship as a community activator coach.

This apprenticeship is recognised by the Chartered Institute for the Management of Sport and Physical Activity (CIMSPA).
If you want to specialise in helping the community with health and wellbeing issues, you may be able to do a public health practitioner degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You could work for organisations like charities, the NHS or local authorities, helping people in communities to live long, healthy and happy lives.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can work towards this role by starting with an advanced apprenticeship as a broadcast production assistant.
You may be able to become a company secretary by first qualifying as a solicitor through a degree aprenticeship.
You can start by doing an advanced apprenticeship in sports coaching.

You could do a lean manufacturing operative intermediate apprenticeship

You may also be able to do an advanced apprenticeship in vehicle upholstery with certain luxury car manufacturers.
You could get into this job through a trade supplier intermediate apprenticeship.
You can get into this career through a prosthetist-orthotist degree apprenticeship.

You could do an engineering technician advanced apprenticeship, which could be used to work in different industries.

You could also do an intermediate or advanced engineering apprenticeship for your particular industry, for example aviation, compressed air and vacuum manufacturing or rail.
You may be able to do a physician associate degree apprenticeship, leading to a master's postgraduate level qualification. It will take around 30 to 36 months to complete.
You may be able to do a public health practitioner degree apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: You may find opportunities in office based, community, or healthcare roles. You could be working for different types of organisations like the NHS, local authorities or charities.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could start by doing an exercise and fitness advanced apprenticeship then move into pilates teaching after completing further training.
You could become a technician after completing an electrical engineering technician advanced apprenticeship.
You can complete a policy officer higher apprenticeship.
You may be able to do a science industry process engineer degree apprenticeship.

You could start by doing a Police Constable Degree Apprenticeship (PCDA). It's a 3 year work-based programme that leads to a degree in Professional Policing Practice.

You can apply through your chosen force.

FurtherInfo.Html:
If you want to work in non-emergency response situations you could do a serious and complex crime investigator degree apprenticeship.

In this role, as well as police forces you could also be employed by organisations like:

  • The National Crime Agency
  • Her Majesty's Revenue and Customs
  • The Ministry of Defence

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can start as a junior shopfitter through an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in construction building wood occupations, or in construction specialist interior systems.
You could do a pharmacy technician advanced apprenticeship.

You can work towards this role through an advanced apprenticeship in agriculture.

This will usually take 18 months to complete. You'll do on-the-job training and spend time with a college or training provider.

You could do a higher apprenticeship in agricultural business management if you already have a lot of farming experience.
You may be able to start by doing a higher apprenticeship as a data analyst.
You may be able to do an archaeological specialist degree apprenticeship.
You could do a furniture manufacturer intermediate apprenticeship or upholsterer advanced apprenticeship.
A common way to become a secretary is to do a business administrator advanced apprenticeship.
You can do an intermediate or advanced creative hair professional apprenticeship.
You could do a paralegal or business administrator advanced apprenticeship.
You could work your way up to management level after completing an advanced apprenticeship in hairdressing. Another option is to do a creative hair professional advanced apprenticeship.
You could get into this job through an advanced apprenticeship as an ambulance support worker.
You can get into this role through an intermediate apprenticeship as a forest operative.
You can complete a laboratory technician or science manufacturing technician advanced apprenticeship.
You can complete an engineering operative intermediate apprenticeship or a metal casting and foundry technician advanced apprenticeship.
You could complete a civil engineer degree apprenticeship and take professional training afterwards to qualify in structural engineering.
You could do an electrical and electronic technical support engineer higher apprenticeship.
You could start by doing a broadcast production assistant advanced apprenticeship and work your way up to a producer role.
You may be able to get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship in warehousing and storage, or trade supplies.
You could do a junior management consultant higher apprenticeship and work your way up as your experience grows.
You can do an intermediate apprenticeship in providing security services.
You could get into this work through a cultural learning and participation officer or museums technician advanced apprenticeship.
You'll need to do an advanced apprenticeship as a senior healthcare support worker, which has a training option for podiatry assistants.

FurtherInfo.Html: When recruiting, employers may select apprentices who have experience as a support worker.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You may be able to get into this job through a digital and technology solutions specialist degree apprenticeship.

You could complete an advanced apprenticeship as a custody and detention officer.

FurtherInfo.Html: It will help if you do your aprenticeship with a company that provides forensic science services, or with a police force that has its own in-house lab facilities.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can work towards this role by starting with an advanced apprenticeship as a junior journalist.
You may be able to start by doing a retailer intermediate apprenticeship.

You could also do an intermediate apprenticeship as a healthcare support worker and then apply for a trainee role in phlebotomy.
You could get into this career through a furniture design technician, bespoke furniture maker or furniture product developer advanced apprenticeship.
You can get into this job through a science manufacturing process operative intermediate apprenticeship.
You could complete a creative venue technician or technical theatre advanced apprenticeship, which have options in sound.

You can get into this job through an intermediate apprenticeship in reprographics.

FurtherInfo.Html: You could then apply to become a pub landlord once you've built up your experience in the drinks trade.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You can work towards this role by doing a public relations assistant higher apprenticeship.

FurtherInfo.Html: After completing your apprenticeship, you could find work with a digital design agency or user research company.

FurtherInfo.Html: You can train with the NHS, and independent and private providers of healthcare services. You can look for training opportunities on NHS Jobs.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You could do an intermediate or advanced apprenticeship in a construction trade like plumbing or carpentry.

You'll need a qualification in the subject you want to teach. Employers will be looking for relevant up-to-date industry experience.

You'll also need to show ability in English, maths and IT.

RelevantSubjects.Html: You may be able to get into this job by doing an insurance professional higher apprenticeship, or degree apprenticeship for senior insurance professionals.

FurtherInfo.Html:
Once you've completed your apprenticeship, you may turn professional or continue as an amateur while you get more experience.

You can find out more from the professional body for your sport.

You may be able to train for similar roles, such as air cartographer in the armed forces.

Royal Air Force
